beer.beer_description:
Brewed for humans who love doggos - and great beer! DoggoBrau is a barking good beer with a tropical aromas and a pawsome, fruity finish. Doggo is an official collaboration with RSPCA Victoria, and 10% of sales of DoggoBrau go directly to RSPCA Vic to help rescue, rehome and rehabilitate dogs in need. 

Brewer tasting notes: A light bodied, easy drinking XPA with subtle citrus and tropical fruit flavours. Well-balanced with a crisp finish 
 
Malt: Pale, Caramalt, Carapils, Wheat 
Hops: El Dorado, Motueka, Sabro, Mosaic, Cryo Simcoe 
Yeast: American Ale 
Colour: Blonde
